            <h3 data-uuid="be8107fc1b0c40efbb464c4a9ab61ab9">Part 2: Write an Explanatory Essay</h3>
            <h6 data-uuid="ee02bb65c79a44dd87283695e50f5268">Historical Context</h6>
            <p data-uuid="1b5f3b2c86f044d2a80cc10ce3929d5e">The
                invention of the cotton gin allowed many southern planters to grow wealthy from
                their cotton production. It also increased the Southâ€™s reliance on slave labor.
                Although rich planters dominated southern society, they made up only a small
                percentage of the population, which also included small farmers, poor whites, and
                enslaved and free African Americans.</p>
            <h6 data-uuid="c12c9e62d079466e8e04880e4bfaa473">Task</h6>
            <p data-uuid="68fd7c101aa340eeb97d09fff13dc217">Southern
                society was divided into groups that varied greatly in social and economic
                power. Yet these groups did not live in isolation from one another. Write an explanatory
                essay in which you discuss connections between different social groups in the
                South.</p>
            <p data-uuid="ab20b2d258de4ec38acff492fd7829bd">Complete the following steps as you plan and compose
                your essay.</p>
            <ol data-uuid="14fc542911b74b3585f39defbee9f470">
                <li data-uuid="fc59b15843c443b0bfe8bab0c456d7fd">
                    Review your notes and sources before you start writing.
                </li>
                <li data-uuid="8d4b4f33b0d34be086fb80e50e8d3bf0">Use
                    at least <i>two</i>&#160;of the sources in Part 1, and develop the essay with
                    relevant, well-chosen text evidence from the documents.<br />
                </li>
                <li data-uuid="7c44052c6fea400ab657e97dd1cd1c69">
                    Cite specific text evidence from each of the sources in your
                    response.
                </li>
                <li data-uuid="59bf5ae2b55c4f01918642d831b686cf">Plan
                    your essay so that it includes an introduction, several body paragraphs, and a
                    concluding paragraph.<br />
                </li>
                <li data-uuid="d2040e78e1e342fc8f4a0606fdca2f3b">Organize your essay in a clear way that focuses on the topic and supports it with explanations and facts.<br />
                </li>
                <li data-uuid="58bf08f1392841189fd1057577aabfbc">Write
                    a conclusion that sums up your ideas and supports the information you present.<br />
                </li>
            </ol>
        </section>
